      "content": "October 21, 2120, CE\n\nThat Day was a change in the life of killers.\n\n“No, No, Nooooo, I will not die, i will... kill him, cut down... his head”. A Final Battle Starts, The Sword and Two-Sided Dragger of that Asura King Kanasura strike and emerging very heavy fire sparks”.\n\nKANSASURA says “This is the right time, put your weapons down and work for me and I will spare your life”.\n\nAditya said “Work for you no way in the hell. My goal is to take your head, and I am not stopping until I chop your head”.\n\nSky was crimson Red, Land full of ruins and blood, dead bodies of all soldiers surrounded everywhere.\n\nThe killer staggered amid the crimson ruins, shadows flickering at his core like a killer’s awakening system, killing intent surging to push him beyond mortal limits. Blood stained the grounds, but his eyes burned with defiance as KANSASURA circled, spear gleaming with infernal light. \n\nKansasura said, “I think you will not understand”.\n\nThe Asura King snarled, lunging forword with blinding speed thrusting the spear straight toword the killer’s midsection, poised to pierce between stomach and chest in a fatal strike that could end it all...\n\n*****\n\nAuthor’s Note\n\nHello, fellow readers! Thanks for reading through this epic prologue. We are two friends who started this project. Our names are Harmanjot Singh Ubhi and Gurtej Singh Jassal. Next chapter is dropping soon stay tuned on our official website."
